Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.39,0:01:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天的味噌湯是兩位的閨女做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望爸爸媽媽會喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.22,0:01:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看起來就不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.63,0:01:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.13,0:01:47.77,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安 鷲尾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.94,0:02:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}媽媽 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇怪 我不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木 你在教室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且馬上就是晨會了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鷲尾 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各位同學 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三之輪銀同學 你遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.78,0:02:29.29,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好痛 很痛耶老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}趕快就座吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小銀 你今天怎麼遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}升上六年級總會有不少事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忘記帶課本了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天的值日生是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}起立
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們能來這裡 都是託神樹大人的福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}向神龕敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們該完成使命了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我還是第一次見到呢 原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神樹大人的結界？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:27.53,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs70\pos(394,200)\alpha&HFF&\t(0,300,0\alpha&F00&)}第{\r\blur2\fs70\alpha&HFF&\t(200,500,0\alpha&F00&)}一{\r\blur2\fs70\alpha&HFF&\t(400,700,0\alpha&F00&)}集
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:27.53,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\alpha&HFF&\t(0,300,0\alpha&F00&)\move(620,480,640,500,0,400)}鷲{\r\blur2\alpha&HFF&\t(200,500,0\alpha&F00&)}尾{\r\blur2\alpha&HFF&\t(400,700,0\alpha&F00&)}須{\r\blur2\alpha&HFF&\t(600,900,0\alpha&F00&)}美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是神樹大人做出的結界內的世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樹海…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟聽到的一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好壯觀 全都是樹耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是大橋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概就是那個沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}連接起這裡與牆壁外的橋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}敵人會從那裡襲擊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好興奮 我們竟然成了勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三之輪 這可不是說著玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就是敵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那傢伙跨過大橋 到達神樹大人身邊時
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}世界就會不復存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得由我們阻止它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來完成使命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蒼茫天地中 森羅萬象拂吾身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明駐吾心 遵吾意願現世間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}獻吾之精魂 萬丈神力齊相助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}獻吾之精魂 承蒙聖力御外敵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的第一次實戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過我們還沒有做配合訓練呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為敵人出現的時間比神諭提及的更早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過應該沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小心應付吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 幹掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三 我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們都站住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:08:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好寬敞 跟訓練時完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想不到這裡原本是城市
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是太奇妙了 鷲尾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從另一側來襲的傢伙 Vertex
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}侵蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}擊退敵人所花的時間越長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原本的世界就會受到越大的負面影響
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}速戰速決
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:08:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}兩位！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看我一斧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想起來這個可以當盾用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟強烈颱風一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想想辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}由我來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鷲尾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種敵人要怎麼對付啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:10:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的弓箭傷害不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三之輪力氣不小 但難以近身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木連我都不知道怎麼應付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到底該如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行動起來就危險…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三之輪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}彈性好強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三 你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}居然全喝下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是獲得了神力的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把水喝乾不費吹灰之力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三 你好厲害 有味道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一開始是汽水 喝著喝著變成烏龍茶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽起來並不好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在要緊的是Vertex
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那傢伙很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}分身神靈太多了 肯定離出口不遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但剛才的攻擊沒有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但不快點 它就要跑出大橋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它要是跑出去 就沒辦法擊退了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拿出鬥志再戰一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我突然有個想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它發現我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}轉來我們這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得抓緊時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}展開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這把長槍能變化成盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}園子真是萬能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}頂著盾牌前進
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木 撐得住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者要看鬥志 把它頂回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一二 一二 一二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來 鷲尾也跟著喊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一二 一二 一二 一二 一二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鷲尾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好難瞄準
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三 我把你甩過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三之輪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嚐到厲害了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鎮魂之儀？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三 你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 我狠狠地給它吃了一頓斧頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多虧有你 儀式開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}平息下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.18,0:15:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}擊退…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來我們不會直接回學校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟了 還穿著室內鞋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剛才拍到樹海了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 照片不是樹海了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看來是拍不下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 鷲尾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}須美？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}須美助？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是險勝而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果只有我一個人 就輸定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:54.58,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷粗黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H545454&\frx356\fry6\frz5.832\pos(250,296)}【沒有朋友】如何與人交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:54.58,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\fs20\1c&H545454&\frz5.832\pos(272,398)\frx356\fry2}「沒有朋友…」這個煩惱很讓人難受吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:54.58,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\fs20\1c&H545454&\frx356\fry2\pos(308,600)\frz6.678}我來教你幾招交朋友的訣竅吧♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:54.58,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷粗黑\bord2\b0\fs30\1c&H6938F2&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frx356\fry2\frz6.678\pos(344,646)}3{\shad2\bord2\1c&HC6DAD9&\3c&H3B4C4F&\4c&H3B4C4F&}大妙招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}昨天也跟各位同學說過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這三位同學肩負著神樹大人指派的重要使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以她們會像昨天那樣 突然從教室消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到時候不要慌張慌亂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}靜下心來 默默為她們三個加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}同學們還是要以平日的課業為重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}使命很辛苦嗎 受了傷很痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這可不能告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小氣鬼～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:29.08,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}告訴我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木 三之輪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以的話…我們去開個慶功宴…好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:18:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…我對平安迎來今天 感到由衷的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在這美好的一天我宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神世紀298年 勇者初戰告捷慶功宴正式開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}祝在座的各位身體健康 學業有成 前途無量…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:19.20,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太死板了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你 須美助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我之前也好幾次想邀請你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但沒能說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以超開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是鷲尾第一次主動邀請我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}確實如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.63,0:18:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都還沒配合演練過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我們第一場戰鬥打得真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也很興奮 有好多想說的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:18:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也是 想要和你們說說話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以邀請了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我以前不是很信任你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}並不是說我討厭你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是我不習慣依賴他人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}須美助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但這樣是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果…只有我一個人 肯定什麼都辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為有你們在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…所以我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我能跟你們當朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們不是已經是了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好開心 我也好想和須美助當朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其實我也不太會交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來須美助的想法跟我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好開心呀 須美助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…乃木
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎麼突然用須美助叫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知不覺就幫你取了個綽號呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你自己都沒自覺喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高興是高興啦 但我不太喜歡這個綽號呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那鷲娜怎麼樣 很有偶像的感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}更不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木也不喜歡「園琳琳」這種叫法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 當我沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想到了 你覺得「鷲鷲」怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就這樣吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請多指教 鷲鷲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 那你們就叫我銀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「三之輪」聽起來好見外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來慶祝交上朋友的今天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家一起去吃這裡超讚的冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}選擇焙茶‧可爾必思口味太對了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三你的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}醬油蠶豆口味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是什麼口味 不過看起來挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抹茶淡淡的苦編織出的口味 真是絕妙的搭配
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼好吃的話 啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種事我是第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好吃 這就是第一次配合工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.55,0:21:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用詞很會讓人想歪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早就想跟朋友做一次這種事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.24,0:22:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鷲鷲你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.10,0:22:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.36,0:22:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好開心呀
Comment: 0,0:22:17.01,0:22:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,OP-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:19.59,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}キミを連れて駆け出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.59,0:22:22.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}誰も追いつけない場所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.20,0:22:27.70,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}今こそ叶えようよ　あの日のやくそく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.80,0:22:42.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}片隅の幸せのつぼみ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.60,0:22:45.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}銀色に輝いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:48.65,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}咲いたら見せてあげよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.83,0:22:53.40,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}見返したアルバムの中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.51,0:22:56.40,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}その頃も今もそう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.51,0:22:58.92,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}一緒に笑ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:04.71,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}南のほうから染まっていく季節
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.71,0:23:07.30,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}ただいまと言ってね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.30,0:23:10.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}きっとすぐに迎えに行く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.39,0:23:13.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}キミを連れて駆け出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:15.72,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}誰も追いつけない場所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:20.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}今こそ叶えようよ　あの日のやくそく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.97,0:23:26.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}ねえ　ずっと待ってたよ　キミのことを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.18,0:23:32.82,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}おかえり　私をもう二度と置いてかないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:19.59,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}牽起你的手 邁開腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.59,0:22:22.20,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}去那片沒有人能夠追上的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.20,0:22:27.70,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}讓我們在這裡 實現那一天許下的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.80,0:22:42.43,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}吐露在角落裡的 一株幸福的花蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.60,0:22:45.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}閃耀著銀露的光澤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:48.65,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}等它綻放 就讓我帶你來看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.83,0:22:53.40,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}翻來覆去過的這本相冊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.51,0:22:56.40,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}記錄著那個時候 還有今天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.51,0:22:58.92,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}我們純真的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:04.71,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}南方吹來的春風 為世界染上了綠意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.71,0:23:07.30,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}記得說聲「我回來了」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.30,0:23:10.39,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}我一定三步並作兩步迎接你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.39,0:23:13.00,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}牽起你的手 邁開腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:15.72,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}去那片沒有人能夠追上的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:20.97,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}讓我們在這裡 實現那一天許下的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.97,0:23:26.18,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}你知道嗎 我一直等待著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.18,0:23:32.82,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}歡迎回來 可不要再丟下我獨自啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.79,0:23:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神世紀298年 這是三位勇者交織成的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:23:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是被神明選中的少女們譜寫的童話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.92,0:24:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明選中的 總是天真無邪的少女們
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.34,0:24:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而在大多數情況下 少女們的結局會是—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.39,0:24:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要舉例就是戰艦長門
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.24,0:24:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.06,0:24:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.80,0:24:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太古怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.91,0:24:19.96,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.06,0:24:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}玩真心話大冒險‧喜歡的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.22,0:24:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有園子在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.56,0:24:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回家前都是合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.35,0:24:26.32,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}終點！
